  "prompt": "What's the best confession you have ever seen on Facebook?",
  "response": "While I don\u2019t have personal experiences or the ability to browse current Facebook posts, I can share that some of the most memorable confessions people often talk about are those that are heartfelt and surprising. For instance, confessions of long-hidden love for a friend, admissions of overcoming personal struggles or mental health challenges, announcements of secret talents or achievements, or heartfelt apologies for past wrongs can all be particularly impactful. It\u2019s usually the honesty and vulnerability that make a confession stand out and resonate with others.",
